import React, {Component} from 'react'
import { Navbar, Nav} from 'react-bootstrap'
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import './header.css'





class Header extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
<>
<Navbar className='navbr' collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark">
  <Navbar.Toggle className='navbrf' aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
  <Navbar.Collapse className="Nb"id="responsive-navbar-nav">
    <Nav className='navli'> 
      <Nav.Link className='Link'><NavLink className='Link1' activeClassName='active' exact to='/'>Home</NavLink></Nav.Link>  
      <Nav.Link className='Link'><NavLink className='Link1'activeClassName='active' exact to='/Ingredients'>Ingredients</NavLink></Nav.Link>  
      <Nav.Link className='Link'><NavLink className='Link1'activeClassName='active' exact to='/Recipe'>Recipe</NavLink></Nav.Link>
      <Nav.Link className='Link'><NavLink className='Link1'activeClassName='active' exact to='/Contact'>Contact</NavLink></Nav.Link>
    </Nav>
  </Navbar.Collapse>
</Navbar>
</>
    )
  }
}
export default Header
